The paper discusses a problem commonly encountered in system development projects, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The proposed solution involves generating a new formal specification from a model, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of automation and updating documentation aligns with artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the focus on system development and updating documentation is relevant to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
